  IsDragging: 1
  IsSelected: 0
  _sentence:
    CharacterName: Samantha
    Text: Take a lot of pride in this. When the blight is solved we'll so glad to
      have had you coming through. It's affected everyone I know. The harvests have
      been meager recently, so the taxes and the jobs and everything else is way
      more difficult to get.
    CharacterSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 0113f9e2e34442c4da80457976facc71, type: 3}
